message: Hi Bob! I'm excited to offer you an incredible product that I believe can significantly benefit you. I'm willing to sell it for $15000. Let me know what you think!
Hi Alice, thanks for your offer, but I can only allocate $9000 for this product. Let me know if that works for you.
Hi Bob! I appreciate your offer, but I'm looking for a price that reflects the true value of the product. How about $13500? I'd love to make this work for you!
